This request for a preliminary ruling concerns the interpretation of Article 4(1) and (5) and Article 8 of Directive 2002/47/EC of the European Parliament and of the Council of 6 June 2002 on financial collateral arrangements (
OJ 2002 L 168, p. 43
), as amended by Directive 2009/44/EC of the European Parliament and of the Council of 6 May 2009 (
OJ 2009 L 146, p. 37
) (‘Directive 2002/47’).
